runtime_sequence:
- resolve EOU ID
- load EOU spec
- validate inputs
- load context manifest
- create run ID
- execute steps
- capture trace
- run deterministic validation
- run judgment audit if needed
- emit output and run report
run_report_required_fields:
- run_id
- eou_id
- eou_version
- input_versions
- status
- warnings
- outputs
- validation
- next_actions
principle: The output of an EOU run is both the intended artifact and evidence about
  the EOU itself.
